[2026-03-15T16:11:36Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01YDfaLFLXjmwSiZkRDqTHVb","type":"tool_result","content":"/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-4-\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-5-**Goal:** Implement a daemon-side post-run evolution pipeline that analyzes workflow history to automatically improve prompts, add validation steps, and refine workflows.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-6-\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md:7:**Architecture:** Multi-stage LLM pipeline (Collector → Classifier → Reflector → Executor branches) running in the daemon after each workflow completion. Three executor branches: Prompt Curator (ACE-style), Script Generator (LLM code gen), DSL Mutator (deterministic Go). Changes auto-applied with JSONL audit trail and snapshots.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-8-\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-9-**Tech Stack:** Go, SQLite, gRPC, TOML config (`github.com/BurntSushi/toml`), existing LLM agent invocation pattern.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-10-\n--\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1060-Create `internal/evolution/reflector.go`:\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1061-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1062-The Reflector sends the collected data (run results, failure logs, knowledge base,\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md:1063:current prompts, workflow) to the LLM with an ACE-style system prompt asking it to:\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1064-1. Examine execution traces for patterns\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1065-2. Extract structured lessons as JSON\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1066-3. Assign confidence levels based on evidence count\n--\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1169-The Curator:\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1170-1. Reads the current prompt file\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1171-2. Sends it to the LLM with the lesson, asking it to merge the lesson as a\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md:1172:   structured bullet/rule (ACE-style curation) while preserving existing content\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1173-3. Creates a snapshot of the original file in `.cloche/evolution/snapshots/`\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1174-4. Writes the LLM's response as the new file content\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1175-5. Returns a `Change` record\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1176-\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md:1177:The LLM system prompt should instruct ACE-style curation: append as a structured\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1178-bullet if new, update in place if it refines an existing rule, deduplicate.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1179-\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md-1180-**Step 4: Run tests**\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-8-completion, applies changes directly to project files, and maintains a structured\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-9-audit trail.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-10-\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md:11:The system draws on the ACE (Agentic Context Engineering) framework for prompt\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-12-evolution — treating prompts as structured, itemized playbooks that accumulate\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-13-lessons rather than monolithic documents that get rewritten.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-14-\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-44-                                   │\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-45-                    ┌──────────────▼──────────────────────┐\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-46-                    │         Reflector (LLM)              │\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md:47:                    │  ACE-style: examines traces,         │\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-48-                    │  extracts structured lessons          │\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-49-                    │  (bullets with metadata)              │\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-50-                    └──────────────┬──────────────────────┘\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-147-  evolution/\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-148-    log.jsonl                   # append-only audit trail (one JSON object per line)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-149-    knowledge/\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md:150:      develop.md                # ACE-style knowledge base for 'develop' workflow\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-151-    snapshots/\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-152-      <timestamp>-<filename>    # pre-change backups for revert\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-153-```\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-219-Handles `prompt_improvement` lessons.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-220-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-221-- Receives the current prompt file content and the lesson\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md:222:- ACE-style curation: merges the lesson into the prompt as a structured\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-223-  bullet/rule\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-224-- Deduplication: checks for semantic overlap with existing bullets; if a lesson\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-225-  refines an existing bullet, it updates in place rather than appending\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-325-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-326-## Knowledge Base Structure\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-327-\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md:328:The knowledge base is an ACE-style structured document — itemized bullets with\ndocs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-329-metadata, not prose. Each bullet tracks usefulness over time:\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-330-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-design.md-331-```markdown\n--\n/workspace/examples/gemini-browser/prompts/implement.md-12-2. Use rustls for TLS. Accept all server certificates (skip verification) —\n/workspace/examples/gemini-browser/prompts/implement.md-13-   Gemini's trust model (TOFU) is out of scope for v1\nexamples/gemini-browser/prompts/implement.md-14-3. Send requests in the format: `gemini://host/path\\r\\n`\nexamples/gemini-browser/prompts/implement.md:15:4. Parse response headers: `<STATUS><SPACE><META>\\r\\n` followed by body\nexamples/gemini-browser/prompts/implement.md-16-5. Handle all status code families:\nexamples/gemini-browser/prompts/implement.md-17-   - 1x INPUT: prompt the user for input, re-request with query string\nexamples/gemini-browser/prompts/implement.md-18-   - 2x SUCCESS: display the body according to the MIME type in META"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01SVVaZSHnQ1ti7Bvo3ZMa2m","session_id":"6cfc7d64-9635-4a5f-9cf9-37398c58dd96","uuid":"